com.oose2015.group13.frontend.battleship

Class UserSettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.oose2015.group13.frontend.battleship.UserSettings

  • public class UserSettings
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a data wrapper class that mirrors the server's com.oose2015.group13.frontend.battleship.UserSettings data object. This exists because the server will return this data in the form of JSon, and the LoginActivity will use a transformer to create this data object for use in the rest of the app.
